Toshiba Enters Wind-Power Businesss Acquiring Convertible Bonds in Unison

-- B y   G o   O n o m i t s u
-- 
2011-05-23T09:18:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-23/toshiba-enters-wind-power-businesss-acquiring-convertible-bonds-in-unison.html
Toshiba Corp. (6502)  plans to enter the wind
power business by acquiring 40 billion won ($36 million) of
convertible bonds in  South Korea ’s Unison Co., according to a
statement on the Japanese company’s website today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
